# {{STYLE_NAME}}

> {{STYLE_DESCRIPTION}}

## What This Does

Changes how Claude formats and styles its responses. When activated via `/output-style {{PRODUCT_SLUG}}`, all subsequent Claude output follows these rules.

## Install

```bash
myclaude install {{PRODUCT_SLUG}}
```

Installs to `.claude/output-styles/{{PRODUCT_SLUG}}.md`.

## Usage

```
/output-style {{PRODUCT_SLUG}}
```

To switch back to default: `/output-style default`

## Requirements

- Claude Code v1.0+

